originalText.text:
Judith K. Coleman is a very competent therapist who empowers you to solve your own issues.
She is a great advocate for you when you’re not at your best,  and supports you to take youself further when you are.  She helps you to see the origin of your issues, not to dwell there though, but to move out of it and supports you in how to get to another level, so not to stagnate.  I do recommend her knowing that the choice of a psychotherapist is a highly personal one especially ongoing.  However, she can help you with shorter terms needs too.
